However, On Dec 9 I Began Having Connection Problems With My Earbuds. So i decided to do what i summes do with amazon, and decide to exchange. This is When I Discovered The Pitfalls of Buying a ‚ÄòRenewed‚Äô Apple Product. 
 First, Unlike Most Amazon Purchasses, There is no return / Exchange Option for Renewed Apple Earpods. There Is, However, Bureaucracy. After Closer Look at My Options and an Hour On The Phone With Amazon and Apple, I Discovered That My Earbud Warranty (With The Sell) Expired on Dec 10.
